ss=\"line\">java    16031 bejond  382u  IPv4 2396178      0t0  TCP *:8643 (LISTEN)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<h6 id=\"附\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#附\"></a> 附:</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>如果知道占用端口进程是java进程，可以使用<code>jps [-v]</code>命令查看，但是没法通过端口查询。</li>\n<li>如果想杀掉进程，可以使用<code>$ kill -9 16031</code>，当然还有根据程序名关闭<code>$ killall java</code>，可以关闭所有java进程，不推荐这么用，风险极大🌚。</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":8,"path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":7,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"},{"name":"Command","slug":"Command","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Command.json"}]}